---
pagination:
  data: locations
  size: 1
  alias: loc
  addAllPagesToCollections: true
permalink: "/{{ loc.slug }}/"
layout: base.njk
eleventyComputed:
  title: "{{ loc.title }}"
  metaDescription: "{{ loc.metaDescription }}"
preloadFonts:
  - /fonts/fraunces-latin-var.woff2
---
<section class="hero hero-local">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow">Land Rover specialist near {{ loc.town }}</div>
    <h1>Your local Land Rover specialist for <em>{{ loc.town }}</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">{{ loc.driveTime }}, {{ loc.route }}. A small independent Land Rover workshop, run by Stuart and David.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="prose-section">
  <div class="wrap prose">
    <p>{{ loc.intro }}</p>

    <h2>What {{ loc.town }} owners come to us for</h2>
    <ul class="emphasis-list">
      {%- for e in loc.emphasis %}
      <li>{{ e }}</li>
      {%- endfor %}
    </ul>
    <p>That's not all we do. See the <a href="/services/">full list of services</a>, from servicing and welding to brakes, suspension and improvements. Whatever your Land Rover needs, give us a ring first and we'll book it in.</p>

    <h2>Getting to the workshop from {{ loc.town }}</h2>
    <p>We're at Orchards, {{ site.address.locality }}, {{ site.address.region }} {{ site.address.postcode }}. {{ loc.route | ucfirst }}. The workshop is by appointment only, so please call <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">{{ site.phoneDisplay }}</a> before you set off.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="area">
  <div class="contours" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div>
      <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <div class="tag">Find us</div>
        <h2>Orchards, Sittingbourne.</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--hero-mute)">A short drive from {{ loc.town }} and the wider area.</p>
      </div>
      <address>
        <b>{{ site.name }}</b>
        {{ site.address.street }}, {{ site.address.locality }}, {{ site.address.region }} {{ site.address.postcode }}<br>
        {{ site.hours.display }}
      </address>
    </div>
    {% include "partials/map.njk" %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="prose-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom:24px">
      <div class="tag">Also nearby</div>
      <h2>Other areas we cover</h2>
    </div>
    <ul class="area-links">
      {%- for other in locations %}{% if other.slug != loc.slug %}
      <li><a href="/{{ other.slug }}/">Land Rover specialist near {{ other.town }}</a></li>
      {%- endif %}{% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
